### 查询部门
GET http://localhost:8080/api/departments

### 新增部门
POST http://localhost:8080/api/departments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "QA",
  "name": "质量保障部"
}

### 分页查询员工
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&keyword=张

### 查询员工详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1

### 新增员工
POST http://localhost:8080/api/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "赵六",
  "phone": "13900000006",
  "email": "zhaoliu@example.com",
  "departmentId": 1,
  "position": "Java开发工程师",
  "hireDate": "2026-05-11",
  "salary": 12000
}

### 修改员工
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/employees/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张三",
  "phone": "13900000001",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "departmentId": 1,
  "position": "高级Java开发工程师",
  "hireDate": "2024-03-01",
  "salary": 18000
}

### 员工离职
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/employees/3

### 上班打卡
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/check-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "note": "到公司"
}

### 下班打卡
POST http://localhost:8080/api/attendance/check-out
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "note": "正常下班"
}

### 查询考勤
GET http://localhost:8080/api/attendance?employeeId=1&startDate=2026-05-01&endDate=2026-05-31

